{
  "stem": "11998.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the first day, they would-- they had clean up wagons that came with us, that they would take the dead prisoners and put them on the wagon to take them with us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After the third or fourth day, they just sat there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just left them there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we got to Gross-Rosen, there was-- the camp was absolutely overfilled.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was horrendous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We got some food rations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were put into barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no beds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to sleep on floors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was hardly enough room to-- to turn around, and terribly congested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And lice were-- just infested with lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Your-- your body was-- like, in the morning, was bitten with-- from-- by-- by the lice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you know, lice are carriers of typhus fever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it-- it was-- it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the morning, we took off our sweater, and we could-- we just kept, you know, shaking out-- the lice were so-- so plentiful, that you could actually shake the sweater, and they would fall down.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it's-- it's hard to believe that, that's how-- how-- how bad-- how bad the situation were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I used to go-- we used to go to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They used to grab people who could still-- you had some flesh on them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, they would take us and put us on cleanup duty.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So we'd have to go and get dead people out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You could let-- go lie down in-- in the-- in the evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And in the morning, you would, like, wake up, and the guy beside you is dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He's died in his sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had to do the cleanup work.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
